    "The same procedure is replicated for each pixel within the image.",
    "Consequently, proceed to the entire image; the features are stored for each fewer image section.",
    "This experiment produces a 9 × 1 matrix for each unit while splitting the picture into 88% units.",
    "Finally, four 8 × 8 units combine to create a 16 × 16 block.",
    "Because the histogram of every single 8 x 8 unit carries out a 9 × 1 structure, the 16 × 16 block as a whole is made up of a single vector that is 36 × 1."
  ],
